      "text": "Un wiꞥſch gahje tam Dee-\nwa Wihran pukkaſ/ un atradde\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch uſ to:\nEij ar mannim Mahjás/ un ehd\nMaisi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tas fazzija : Es ne\nwarru ar tewin atpakkaſ gree-\nstees/ nedß ar tewim ect/ es arrt\nne ehdiſchu Maisi/ nedß dſerſchu\nar tewim Uhdeni ſchinni Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo uſ man irr runnahts\nzaur ta KUNGA Wahrdn/ tew\nne buhs Maisi ehſt/ nedß tur Uh-\nDeni dſert/ tew ne buhs atpakkaſ\ngreestees pa to Zeltu no-eedams/\nuſ ko tu effi nahzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija uſ to:\nEs efmu arri weens Praweets\ntà patt kà tu/ un weens Enge-\nlis irr ar man runnajs zaur ta\nKUNGA Wahrdn/ fazzidams:\nWedd winnu ar tew atpakkaſ\ntawá Namina / ka tas Maisi\nehḍ/ un Uhdeni dſerr. Bet wiꞥſch\nmelloja tam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tà atgreesaſs wiꞥſch ar\nto atpakkaſ/ un ehde ar to Mai-\nſi winna Namina / un dſehre\nUhdeni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un teem pee Gałda feh-\nschoht / notikte ta KUNGA\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wahrds uſ to Praweetu / to\nwinnu bij atpakkaſ weddis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fauze. uſ to Deetw\nWibru / kas no Juhda bij na-\nzis/ fazzidams: Ta fakka ta\nKUNGS: Tapehz ka tu\nKUNGA Muttei effi prettitu\nrejees/ un winna Pawehlefch\nnn ne darrijs/ ko tas KUNG(\ntaiws Deewa tew pawehlejs/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet effi atpakkaſ greese\nun Maisi ehdis/ un uhdeni jch\nWeetá dsehris/ no ka wiꞥſch u\ntew bij runnajs: Tev ne bu\nMaisi ehſt/ nedß uhdeni dſert\ntad taws Lihktis ne nahks tan\nTehwu Kappa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu wiꞥſch bij Ma-\nehdis un dsehris/ tad likke win-\ntam to Ehseli fedloht / (proht\ntam Praweetam/ ko wiꞥſch b\natpakkaſ weddis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad negahje wiꞥſch/ u\nweens Lauwa atradde to uſ Ze-\ntu/ un nokawe to / un win-\nLihktis gulleja uſ Zeltu mest-\nun tas Ehselis stahweja pee t\nun tas Lauwa stahweja pee\nLihka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un rangi/ kad Laudisfe\nzen gabje/ un redſeja to Lihki\nZeltu mestu / un to Lauwu p\nLihka stahwim/ tad nahze te-\nun fluddinaja to tai Pilssfaht\nkur kas wezzajs Praweets dſi\nwoja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tas Praweets/ k\nwinnu no ta Zelta bij atpak-\nweddis/to dſirdeja/fazzija win-\nWiꞥſch irr tas Deewa Wihr\n"
    }
